{"tid":252767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衣著暴露可減低女性被強姦機會","createTime":"2017-05-21T22:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T02:19:57.000Z","uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4152a98bf284ad1b15d908530eaf28afe368bf6","tid":252767,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T22:42:12.000Z","msg":"一般人對被性侵的女性，或許第一個想法就是「她當時穿什麼」，反而不是對安慰她們、了解她們的冤屈，而美國一位大學學生，對世人普遍認為女性遭性侵一定是穿太暴露的刻板印象不滿，所以訪問了一些受性侵的女學生，拍下她們當時的穿著做平反。<br />\n據英國媒體《METRO》報導，美國阿卡迪亞大學(Arcadia University)學生坎巴雷利（Katherine Cambareri)，不滿許多人的觀念上，認為遭性侵的女性穿著一定是很暴露的，於是找了願意接受採訪、曾遭受性侵的女性，提供她們當時所穿著的服裝。而從照片中可看到，大部分的女性穿著都相當保守且樸素的衣物，顯示出想性侵妳的人，根本不會在意穿什麼服裝。<br />\n坎巴雷利表示「一般人會有刻板印象認為被性侵的女性都是穿著暴露衣物的，我想結束這樣的指責，性侵犯會襲擊女性，不是因為她們的服裝」，而坎巴雷利拍攝的照片，也將在阿卡迪亞大學美術館展出。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導)<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160507/640_3f277d84b3fa8c09f332515249de2af6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160507%2F640_3f277d84b3fa8c09f332515249de2af6.jpg&h=446c0ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160507/640_e7bc7a04634161ffcbcea2e27b851b22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160507%2F640_e7bc7a04634161ffcbcea2e27b851b22.jpg&h=96a209b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160507/640_2cc79ff6ab7503bea19484a45cee4be9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160507%2F640_2cc79ff6ab7503bea19484a45cee4be9.jpg&h=87d62837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160507/640_2a1b4d3b26875ee80a7300ec9c81ee44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160507%2F640_2a1b4d3b26875ee80a7300ec9c81ee44.jpg&h=37069a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews